<messaging:emailTemplate subject="PR PT Contract Approval Request - {!Relatedto.Name}" recipientType="User" relatedToType="EUR_CRM_Contract__c"><messaging:HtmlEmailBody >    Dear Approver,    <br/>    <br/>    Um novo acordo criado por {!RelatedTo.CreatedBy.Name} no dia {!RelatedTo.CreatedDate} aguarda a sua aprovação.<br/><br/>    Detalhes do acordo abaixo:<br/>      <apex:outputPanel layout="none"> <br/> <table> <tr>            <td>                <strong>Numero de Acrodo: </strong>            </td>            <td>               {!Relatedto.Name}             </td>        </tr>         <tr>            <td>                <strong>Nome do Cliente : </strong>            </td>            <td>               {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Account__r.Name}             </td>        </tr>         <tr>            <td>                <strong>Contato do cliente : </strong>            </td>            <td>                {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Contact__r.Name}            </td>        </tr>            <tr>            <td>                <strong>Tipo de acordo : </strong>            </td>            <td>                {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Contract_Type__c}            </td>        </tr>        <tr>            <td>                <strong>Status do acordo : </strong>            </td>            <td>                {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Status__c}            </td>        </tr>        <tr>            <td>                <strong>Activo : </strong>            </td>            <td>                {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Active__c}            </td>        </tr>        <tr>            <td>                <strong>Obrigatoriedade de auditoria : </strong>            </td>            <td>                {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Audit_Mandatory__c}            </td>        </tr>                          <tr>            <td>                <strong>Data de inicio : </strong>            </td>            <td>                <apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}">                    <apex:param value="{!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Start_Date__c}" />                </apex:outputText>            </td>        </tr>         <tr>            <td>                <strong>Data de Fim : </strong>            </td>            <td>                <apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}">                    <apex:param value="{!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_End_Date__c}" />                </apex:outputText>            </td>        </tr>         <tr>            <td>                <strong>Duração do acrodo (meses) : </strong>            </td>         <td>                {!Relatedto.EUR_CRM_Contract_Duration_month__c}            </td>        </tr>        <tr>            <td>                <strong>Valor do acrodo : </strong>            </td>            <td>               <apex:outputText value="{0,number,###0.00}">EUR&nbsp;<apex:param value="{!relatedto.EUR_CRM_Contract_Actual_Amount__c}" /></apex:outPutText>            </td>        </tr>         <tr>            <td>                <strong>Valor do acordo por ano    : </strong>            </td>            <td>               <apex:outputText value="{0,number,###0.00}">EUR&nbsp;<apex:param value="{!relatedto.EUR_CRM_Contract_Actual_Avg_Annual_Amt__c   }" /></apex:outPutText>            </td>        </tr>     <tr>            <td>                <strong>Is this contract material? </strong>            </td>            <td>               <apex:outputText value="{0,number,###0.00}"><apex:param value="{!relatedto.EUR_CRM_Is_this_contract_material__c}" /></apex:outPutText>            </td>        </tr>                <tr>            <td>                <strong>Este acordo é rentável? </strong>            </td>           <td>               <apex:outputText value="{0,number,###0.00}"><apex:param value="{!relatedto.EUR_CRM_Is_this_contract_profitable__c}" /></apex:outPutText>            </td>        </tr>          </table>       </apex:outputPanel>   <br/>   Para aprovar ou rejeitr este acordo aceda a este link : <a href="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_340, FIND(".com/",$Api.Partner_Server_URL_340)+3)}/{!relatedTo.Id}">        {!relatedTo.Name}    </a>   <br/>Este acordo foi submetido por {!Relatedto.CreatedBy.Name} <apex:outputText rendered="{!Relatedto.CreatedBy.MobilePhone != null}"> ({!Relatedto.CreatedBy.MobilePhone}) </apex:outputText> </messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>